definitions.definition: The state , position , or fact of being a god or God .

examples: You may leave out where you live and use either initials or an alias, since gods, buddhas and other divinities look only at our hearts.

definitions.definition: A celestial being inferior to a supreme God but superior to man .
The study of religion or religions.
A type of confectionery made with egg whites , corn syrup , and white sugar .

main_definition: ( uncountable ) The state , position , or fact of being a god or God . [from 14th c.]
secondary_definitions: A celestial being inferior to a supreme God but superior to man .
